Ing '''talampune''' (''Datura metel'') metung yang yerbang pilmihan (''perennial'') a balamu [[palungpung]] a maki karaniwang lugal king Ingles a '''angel's trumpet''', '''devil's trumpet''', ampong '''metel'''. 

Tutubu ya king ilang ing talampune kareng anggang malisangan a dake nng yate, at tatanam de king mabilug a yatu uling kareng kayang katangian antimong sangkap (''chemical property'') ampong antimong tanaman a pampasanting o ''ornamental''. Minuna yang milarawan kapamilatan nang [[Linnaeus]] anyang 1753. E siguradu nung nukarin ing orihinal nang lugal.<ref name='Preissel'>{{cite book | last = Preissel | first = Ulrike | authorlink = | coauthors = Hans-Georg Preissel | title = Brugmansia and Datura: Angel's Trumpets and Thorn Apples | publisher = Firefly Books | date = 2002 | location = Buffalo, New York | pages = 120–123 | url = http://www.amazon.com/Brugmansia-Datura-Angels-Trumpets-Apples/dp/1552095584 | doi = | id = | isbn = 1-55209-598-3 }}</ref>

Ing tanaman metung yang banwahan The plant is an (''annual'') yerbang miraras king anggang 3&nbsp;ft. kátas. Mabwak yang bagya, at maki maralumdum a kule ubing suli ampong bulung a malapad a tulungkaba (''oval'') a maralumdum muring ubi king kule. Mabanglu la reng sampagang 6-8 in. a miyayaliwa itsura, at malyaring lang tunggal (''single'') o dobli. Deng kule manibat la king maputi angga king ''cream'', dilo, malutu ampong kule ubi. Ing The ''seed capsule'' mitatakpan yang dakal a bukul a katabas apa  is covered with numerous (''conical'') ampong ditak a suksuk.<ref name="Preissel"/> Kawangis ne ning ''[[Datura inoxia|D. inoxia]]'', oneng ing ''D. metel'' maki bulung yang alus makinis, ampong bungang bukul-bukul has almost glabrous leaves and fruits that are (''knobby''), oneng e masuksuk.  Ing ''D. inoxia'' laganas yang mitatakpan yang malambut ampong makinis a bwak, at maki bunga yang masuksuk. 

